_sText:
This is a surf skill map.
There are 3 levels. The first level is easy, 2nd is harder and 3 is really hard.
There is a time limit of 2 minutes, then everyone gets tele to jail. If you make it to the end, you get a ak.

Best results for:
sv_airaccelerate 100 - 200

Note: This is my first surf map that i used lighting, so if you are wondering why its so dark in some areas, thats pretty much why.
Enjoy!
